{"tid":280135,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[The Grand Tour] Richard Hammond又炒車","createTime":"2017-06-12T00:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T17:43:35.000Z","uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b964f1b5a42c864785eae275d9784d112ab94ae3","tid":280135,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"Richard Hammond 嚴重炒車 電動車付之一炬<br />\n六月 11, 2017<br />\n<br />\n備受車迷歡迎的 Amazon Prime 節目《The Grand Tour》，上星期才宣佈會在 10 月播映第二季，節目正在密鑼緊鼓拍攝中，昨日卻發生了嚴重事故。三位主持在瑞士拍攝期間，Richard Hammond 駕駛的電動超跑炒車，Hammond 的膝蓋骨折，而超跑則燒成廢鐵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/0611-1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F0611-1a.jpg&h=2680bfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時 Hammond 駕駛著由克羅地亞車廠研發的 Rimac Concept One 電動車，正在瑞士亨貝格參予一項 Hill Climb 賽車活動時出事，電動車在 Hammond 由車內逃離後就起火。拍攝團隊表示 Hammond 未有嚴重受傷，清醒並能夠說話，意外發生後馬上由醫療直升機送往醫院檢查，及後發現膝部骨折。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://b6c18f286245704fe3e9-05e2055f4cd9122af02914269431c9f6.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/16186270_richard-hammond-crashed-rimac-concept_t8c15481c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fb6c18f286245704fe3e9-05e2055f4cd9122af02914269431c9f6.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com%2F16186270_richard-hammond-crashed-rimac-concept_t8c15481c.gif&h=cfb49c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然團隊表示撞車起因未明，尚待有關方面調查，不過有圍觀市民拍攝到意外一刻的畫面，當時汽車在一個彎位失控滾落路旁的草地並翻側。Hammond 並非首次在拍攝汽車節目時出意外，約 11 年前拍攝《Top Gear》時發生嚴重車禍差點喪命，今年年初在莫桑比克拍攝電單車場面時又再發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n來源：recode"},{"pid":"de3b060748a998e330eec012371c8a41d2b8870a","tid":280135,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"佢又要俾人串唔知幾耐<br />\n不過JC同May一路都話佢手車好aggressive"},{"pid":"f6e1cf3a0a112240770b831779160a9f52d97f32","tid":280135,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PdrTn15JYgc\" data-sr-url